title: Black Eyed Kids: Alien Intruders?
description:
In this second part of a two part episode on Black Eyed Kids, Dave and Tim explpore the BEK's alien side and talk with Experiencers Jason Offutt and Whitley Streiber as they share their personal stories and stories they have collected from others. Plus, a brand new Theater Of The Mind!

Jason Offutt: http://www.jasonoffutt.com/

Whitley Streiber: http://www.strieber.com/
